        // ì¹´ë©”ë¼ ì´ë™ - ì‹¤ì œ ë³€ê²½ì´ ìˆì„ ë•Œë§Œ ìˆ˜í–‰
        let isCameraChanged = context.coordinator.prevCenterCoordinate != centerCoordinate || context.coordinator.prevZoomLevel != zoomLevel
